# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ============================================================================

# 1. Array Lengths: LINK_LABELS and LINK_URLS must have the same number of entries
# 2. Indices: All indices (for LINK_DISABLED) start at 0
# 3. Descriptions: Can be empty strings if you don't want tooltips
# 4. Emojis: Use any emoji you like in labels for visual identification
# 5. URL Format: URLs should start with https://, http://, or file://
# 6. Reload: After editing, reload waybar: killall -SIGUSR2 waybar
